{"id":641481,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/04/贴着创可贴的太史毛球：那些黑暗的秘密/","date":"2020-04-13T05:08:14Z","modified":"2020-04-13T10:56:38Z","title":"贴着创可贴的太史毛球：那些黑暗的秘密","content":"<p>CDT编者按：近日鲍毓明案的报道在网络热传，微博网友“贴着创可贴的太史毛球”在微博写下自己7岁左右被表哥性侵的黑暗秘密，在几个小时后，她收到上千条私信，几乎全是这样的黑暗秘密。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@贴着创可贴的太史毛球 ：几个小时，上千条私信，全是黑暗的秘密。生父、继父、养父、爷爷/姥爷、堂表哥、老师、邻居……也有一两条是男孩被阿姨侵犯。全部是没能说出口烂在心里的屈辱回忆。几百个女孩都在强调“对！一模一样！我当时也假装爱上了他！”、“我也有亲近他的行为！”可是，我们不是自愿的。（由于私信数量太多，我只能选取了一些发出，而且不确定每一条发出都征得了同意，因为这里系统顺序有点乱。如未征得同意请私信我删除）</p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641482\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/0-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"2759\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/0-scaled.jpg 464w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/0-768x4240.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/0-371x2048.jpg 371w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641483\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/屏幕快照-2020-04-12-下午9.36.31.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/屏幕快照-2020-04-12-下午9.36.31.png 805w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/屏幕快照-2020-04-12-下午9.36.31-300x268.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/屏幕快照-2020-04-12-下午9.36.31-768x685.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-641484\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"693\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-27.jpg 866w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-27-217x300.jpg 217w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-27-739x1024.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/04/1-27-768x1064.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n